Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.87,0:00:09.86,Default,,0,0,0,,为了考试来东京
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.87,0:00:12.93,Default,,0,0,0,,是处男
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.88,0:00:18.94,Default,,0,0,0,,话不多
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.88,0:00:22.94,Default,,0,0,0,,兴趣是看漫画
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.95,0:00:27.89,Default,,0,0,0,,最近交了女友
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.89,0:00:34.95,Default,,0,0,0,,是后辈
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.83,0:00:39.89,Default,,0,0,0,,是她跟我告白
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.83,0:00:43.89,Default,,0,0,0,,终于有了脱处的机会
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.85,0:00:59.91,Default,,0,0,0,,帮我解开内衣
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.94,0:01:24.88,Default,,0,0,0,,不是应该很简单吗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.84,0:01:58.90,Default,,0,0,0,,不用了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.85,0:02:08.91,Default,,0,0,0,,我不喜欢技术差的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.86,0:02:12.92,Default,,0,0,0,,我要回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.86,0:02:20.92,Default,,0,0,0,,越来越害怕女生
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.87,0:02:28.93,Default,,0,0,0,,后来吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.94,0:02:31.88,Default,,0,0,0,,当然被甩了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.83,0:02:51.89,Default,,0,0,0,,真赞
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.84,0:03:03.90,Default,,0,0,0,,跟他常玩在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.91,0:03:10.85,Default,,0,0,0,,他也是处男
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.92,0:03:16.86,Default,,0,0,0,,目前在看性爱教学
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.93,0:03:28.87,Default,,0,0,0,,也让我的生活变得有趣
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.87,0:03:35.93,Default,,0,0,0,,内衣很重要
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.95,0:03:42.88,Default,,0,0,0,,有那么难吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.95,0:03:46.89,Default,,0,0,0,,男优一下就解开了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.89,0:03:49.95,Default,,0,0,0,,你完全不懂
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.83,0:04:00.89,Default,,0,0,0,,你大嫂奶很大
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.84,0:04:06.90,Default,,0,0,0,,真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.84,0:04:14.90,Default,,0,0,0,,也是啦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.92,0:04:19.85,Default,,0,0,0,,借他的内衣来练习吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.92,0:04:25.86,Default,,0,0,0,,不行啦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.93,0:04:29.86,Default,,0,0,0,,偷偷来就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.87,0:04:38.93,Default,,0,0,0,,没问题吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.94,0:04:41.87,Default,,0,0,0,,走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.95,0:04:53.89,Default,,0,0,0,,快点
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.84,0:05:15.90,Default,,0,0,0,,你搞错目标了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.85,0:05:23.91,Default,,0,0,0,,是这啦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.86,0:05:33.92,Default,,0,0,0,,麻烦你了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.87,0:05:43.93,Default,,0,0,0,,真棒
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.88,0:05:55.94,Default,,0,0,0,,这也太大
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.89,0:06:05.95,Default,,0,0,0,,要快点才行
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.94,0:06:57.88,Default,,0,0,0,,解不开
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.89,0:07:12.95,Default,,0,0,0,,时间差不多了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.90,0:07:24.84,Default,,0,0,0,,就这样吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.92,0:07:38.85,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.92,0:07:42.85,Default,,0,0,0,,有东西落在我房间吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.93,0:07:50.86,Default,,0,0,0,,想说要练习一下
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.93,0:07:56.87,Default,,0,0,0,,就是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.89,0:08:17.95,Default,,0,0,0,,什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.90,0:08:27.83,Default,,0,0,0,,练习
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.84,0:08:34.90,Default,,0,0,0,,解开吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.92,0:08:45.85,Default,,0,0,0,,是挂钩吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.93,0:08:55.86,Default,,0,0,0,,这是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.93,0:08:59.86,Default,,0,0,0,,性爱教学
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.84,0:10:50.90,Default,,0,0,0,,挂钩啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.91,0:10:55.85,Default,,0,0,0,,是大人了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.85,0:11:00.91,Default,,0,0,0,,没兴趣才奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.92,0:11:07.86,Default,,0,0,0,,以前就觉得他很可爱
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.94,0:11:19.87,Default,,0,0,0,,老公你回来了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.88,0:11:26.94,Default,,0,0,0,,好像有捉到感觉了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.88,0:11:34.94,Default,,0,0,0,,是听错了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.92,0:14:24.86,Default,,0,0,0,,你做什么
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.93,0:14:36.87,Default,,0,0,0,,你怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.88,0:14:45.94,Default,,0,0,0,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.87,0:15:42.93,Default,,0,0,0,,你怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.94,0:15:51.88,Default,,0,0,0,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.95,0:16:03.89,Default,,0,0,0,,你怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.91,0:16:30.85,Default,,0,0,0,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.92,0:16:34.85,Default,,0,0,0,,你在做什么
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.93,0:16:44.86,Default,,0,0,0,,住手
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.96,0:17:18.90,Default,,0,0,0,,真的很抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.90,0:17:27.84,Default,,0,0,0,,其实
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.84,0:17:30.90,Default,,0,0,0,,以前有不好的经历
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.85,0:17:38.91,Default,,0,0,0,,之前有交女友
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.92,0:17:47.86,Default,,0,0,0,,但紧要关头时
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.93,0:17:51.86,Default,,0,0,0,,钩子解不开
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.87,0:17:56.93,Default,,0,0,0,,后来就被甩了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.96,0:18:19.89,Default,,0,0,0,,解不开啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.96,0:18:25.90,Default,,0,0,0,,真的很抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.92,0:18:54.86,Default,,0,0,0,,她人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.93,0:19:00.87,Default,,0,0,0,,可能在念书吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.87,0:19:05.93,Default,,0,0,0,,这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.89,0:19:21.95,Default,,0,0,0,,你在看什么 没什么啦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.89,0:19:27.95,Default,,0,0,0,,在看内衣
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.90,0:19:31.83,Default,,0,0,0,,这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.90,0:19:35.83,Default,,0,0,0,,我先睡了 晚安
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.85,0:19:48.91,Default,,0,0,0,,这样就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.92,0:19:55.85,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.87,0:20:12.93,Default,,0,0,0,,第一次穿这种
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.90,0:20:44.84,Default,,0,0,0,,前面的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.93,0:21:10.86,Default,,0,0,0,,这样吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.89,0:21:43.83,Default,,0,0,0,,扣住了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.84,0:21:52.90,Default,,0,0,0,,这样就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.91,0:22:01.85,Default,,0,0,0,,可以进去吗
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.85,0:22:08.91,Default,,0,0,0,,要进去了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.87,0:22:24.93,Default,,0,0,0,,那个
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.94,0:22:29.87,Default,,0,0,0,,我想过了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.95,0:22:37.88,Default,,0,0,0,,我能帮你做的事
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.90,0:22:58.84,Default,,0,0,0,,我来陪你练习吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.91,0:23:10.85,Default,,0,0,0,,这样才能往前
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.86,0:23:21.92,Default,,0,0,0,,真的? 真的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.87,0:23:31.93,Default,,0,0,0,,菜奈实
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.94,0:23:36.88,Default,,0,0,0,,要温柔一点啦
