Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.96,0:23:58.90,Default,,0,0,0,,揉揉吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.83,0:24:01.82,Default,,0,0,0,,恩
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.83,0:24:04.89,Default,,0,0,0,,要温柔一点
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.91,0:24:11.84,Default,,0,0,0,,就是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:24:34.93,0:24:37.87,Default,,0,0,0,,同时亲亲吧
Dialogue: 0,0:24:40.94,0:24:43.88,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:24:59.89,0:25:02.95,Default,,0,0,0,,很厉害嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:26:13.83,0:26:16.89,Default,,0,0,0,,你看
Dialogue: 0,0:26:31.85,0:26:34.91,Default,,0,0,0,,很厉害啊
Dialogue: 0,0:27:08.96,0:27:11.89,Default,,0,0,0,,是前面
Dialogue: 0,0:27:21.90,0:27:24.84,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么在前面
